Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.81,0:03:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,良     医
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.81,0:03:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一季  第七集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什么  系统崩溃了吗\NCome on. Is the system down?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.74,0:00:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这儿没问题\NWorked fine for me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等不了了\NI don't have time for this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.77,0:00:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么了\NHow you doing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.83,0:00:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电脑故障了\NThe computer is not working.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.42,0:00:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我问的不是这个\NThat's not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道  我没事\NI know. I'm fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有个病患因你的操作丧命\NA patient died because of something you did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.85,0:00:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你现在绝对不是「没事」\NI think it's safe to say the one thing you are not is "Fine."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在调整\NI'm dealing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.21,0:00:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在怎么调整\NHow exactly are you dealing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.89,0:00:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在继续工作\NI'm getting back to work,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要给糖尿病变脚趾做清创\NI have a diabetic toe to debride,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.64,0:00:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经放下了\Nand I'm putting it behind me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.07,0:00:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是怎么做到放下的\NHow do you do that -- put it behind you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.22,0:00:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往前看啊\NBy moving forward.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-谢谢你关心  -不用谢\N- I appreciate your concern. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.39,0:01:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我给你预约一次心理咨询吧\NI'm gonna make an appointment for you for grief counseling.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.52,0:01:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫翰医生  她很擅长给经历重压事件的\NDr. Mohan -- She's an expert in dealing with hospital staff
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.75,0:01:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,医务人员做心理疏导\Nwho have experienced stressful events.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.49,0:01:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没必要\NThat's not necessary.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.24,0:01:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你同意自己遭遇「重压事件」了吗\NYou agree you had a "Stressful event"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.99,0:01:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我很欣慰\NAnd while I am comforted
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.69,0:01:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说已经放下过去往前看了\Nby your commitment to move forward by not looking back,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.51,0:01:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但还是希望你去见见莫翰医生\NI still want you to see Dr. Mohan.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果她说你没事了\NIf she says that you are fine,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有那样  你才能重回手术台\Nthen -- and only then -- can you go back to surgery.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.07,0:01:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,系统现在好了\NIt's working now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.96,0:01:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你得有耐心\NYou just have to be patient.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.40,0:01:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心率36\NHeart rate 36.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.98,0:01:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再推十毫克吗啡  准备滴注硝酸甘油\NPush another five milligrams of morphine and prep a nitro drip.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.26,0:01:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻准备阿托品\NWe need atropine on board stat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.11,0:01:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么情况\NWhat do you got for me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.95,0:01:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心肌梗塞并伴有严重心动过缓\NAn MI with severe bradycardia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.66,0:01:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注射了阿司匹林和硝酸甘油\NHe's had aspirin, nitro,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在打算给他注射实际量的阿托品\Nand now we're trying to give him a real rate with atropine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.54,0:01:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心脏科医生看过了吗\NCardiology see him?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.47,0:01:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的起搏器坏了\NHe's got a broken pacemaker
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能需要疏通他的冠状动脉\Nand probably needs his coronary arteries cleared --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该要做三支冠状动脉分流术  但你才是专家\Nfeels like a triple bypass, but you're the expert.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心衰定量标志物太高了\NBNP is sky high.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.25,0:02:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看到了什么\NWhat do you see?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的心室几乎不能泵血了\NHis ventricles are barely pumping.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.04,0:02:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有过两次严重的心肌梗塞\NHe's had two massive prior MIs.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.57,0:02:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心力衰竭末期\NEnd stage heart failure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.68,0:02:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的心脏无法修复了\NHis heart's way beyond repair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.48,0:02:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们该怎么做\NWhat are our options?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.29,0:02:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他已经73岁了\NHe's 73 years old.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个年龄肯定没法获批做移植\NHis age is an absolute contraindication for transplant.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-他要死了  -至少现在还没死\N- He's dying. - Well, he's not dead yet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.78,0:02:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有呢\NWhat else?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.81,0:02:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心脏再同步化治疗如何\NHow about cardiac resynchronization?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.42,0:02:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让两边心室健康的部位能同步正常运行\NThat will get what's left of both ventricles working together.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.54,0:02:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用双心室起搏器\NA biventricular pacer?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.92,0:02:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以让他在剩下的几个月里好受一些\NIt should make him feel a little better in the few months he's got left.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心率再往下降  就会心脏骤停\NHis rate drops any lower, he'll arrest.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.89,0:02:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克莱尔  准备切开颈静脉安放临时起搏器\NClaire, prep his jugular to float in a temporary pacemaker.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.14,0:02:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肖恩  通知导管室\NShaun, call up to the cath lab
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他们预估多久才能准备好\Nand have them get an estimate on how long it'll take
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,双心室起搏器\Nto get the bi-pacer in house.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.36,0:02:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有问题吗\NSomething wrong?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.78,0:02:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有\NNot at all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是早上咖啡喝多了\NJust a little bit too much coffee this morning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那继续  动手吧\NLet's go. Do it now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绑住他\NRestraints, please!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.15,0:03:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不想被针头扎伤\NI don't want to get stuck with a needle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们吓到他了\NYou're scaring him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们吓到他了\NYou're scaring him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五毫克氟哌丁苯\NHaldol, five milligrams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.65,0:03:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们吓到他了\NYou're scaring him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-你是谁  -肖恩·莫菲医生\N- Who are you? - Dr. Shaun Murphy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这位病患有精神问题  莫菲医生\NThis patient is psychotic, Dr. Murphy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他没有精神问题\NHe's not psychotic.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不喜欢被别人碰\NYou don't like people touching you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他没有精神问题  他有自闭症\NHe's not psychotic. He's autistic.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是位非常配合的病患\NYou're being an excellent patient.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了  弄完了\NOkay. We're finished.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.29,0:04:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟我...\NYou're s-same as...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.67,0:04:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一样\Nme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以松开他的手吗\NCan we release his hands?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.47,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫菲医生  手能松开吗\NDr. Murphy? His hands?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来了  孩子  爸爸妈妈来了\NI'm here, son -- Mom and Dad are here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们可以松开他的手  他不会伤到你们\NYou can let go of his hands. He won't hurt you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.13,0:04:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下错站了  下错站了\NWrong stop. Wrong stop.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁能告诉我发生了什么\NCan someone tell me what happened?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.19,0:04:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利亚姆的前额有5.4厘米的撕裂伤\NLiam has a 5.4 centimeter laceration on his forehead,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是摔倒了\Nprobably from a fall.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.96,0:04:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伤口用五毫升1%的利多卡因处理了\NThe wound was infiltrated with five milliliters of 1% lidocaine...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.20,0:04:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用5-0的普理灵缝线单点间断缝合了七针\N7 -- 7 single-interrupted 5-0 Prolene sutures.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会留下小疤痕\NHe will have a small scar,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但伤口不会有其他长期影响\Nbut no other long-term effects from this injury.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我儿子的主治医生\NYou're my son's doctor.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对  我是肖恩·莫菲  「恩赐」的「恩」\NI am. Dr. Shaun Murphy -- "Shaun" with a U.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷路了  迷路了  迷路了\NGot lost -- got lost, got lost, got lost, got lost!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.93,0:05:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-对对  但你没事了  -迷路了  迷路了\N- Yes, yes. Yes. But you're okay. - Got lost. Got lost, got lost.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以后不坐那趟公交了\NYou won't be taking that bus again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯光太亮了\NThis light is too bright.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.79,0:05:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里让他很焦虑  我们能带他回家吗\NThese rooms make him anxious. Can we take him home?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.97,0:05:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行\NNo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的儿子得黄疸了\NYour son is jaundiced,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.18,0:05:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,触摸和发热会让他的右腹肌肉紧张\Nclenching his right abdominal muscles when touched and febrile.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.89,0:05:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不能回家\NHe should not go home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎么在这\NWhy am I here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的起搏器故障了\NYour pacemaker malfunctioned.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心脏病发作了\NYou had a heart attack.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想我听得懂\NI...I think I get that part.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你邻居的园丁看到你倒在屋里的地板上\NYour neighbor's gardener saw you on the ground inside your house --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.72,0:05:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是报警  救了你一命\Ncalled 911, saved your life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.96,0:05:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我得记着谢谢他\NWell, I must remember to thank him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你多大了\NHow old are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吗\NMe?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道我多大了\NI know how old I am.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,28岁\NI'm 28.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.47,0:06:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们给你准备了双心室起搏器\NWe have, uh, a biventricular pacer on its way,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会让你好受很多\Nand it's gonna make you feel a lot better.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.93,0:06:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗\NIs it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.77,0:06:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一会儿回来给你准备手术\NI will be back to prep you for surgery.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利亚姆的胆红素和肝酶都增高了\NLiam has elevated bilirubin and liver enzymes,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白细胞23\Na white cell count of 23.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.57,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腹部超声波结果显示胆管肿大\NAbdominal ultrasound shows dilatation of the bile ducts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是上行性胆道炎\NSounds like ascending cholangitis --
