Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.62,0:20:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我活够了\NI've lived.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.91,0:20:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有过得体的工作\NI've had decent jobs,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也失过业\Nand I've had jobs that went nowhere.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.95,0:21:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住过好房子\NHad a good roof over my head,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.45,0:21:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也失去了好房子\Nand I've had that good roof taken away from me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.62,0:21:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爱过一个女孩  然后我结了婚\NI loved a girl, and I got married.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.69,0:21:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,度过我人生中最幸福的二十年\NThe 20 happiest years of my life...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后她去世了\Nthen she died.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我又孤身一人了\NAnd now I'm alone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛苦地活着\Nand in pain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.22,0:21:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该结束了\NFeels like the end of the story.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.96,0:21:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白\NI understand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.17,0:21:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗\NYeah?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.26,0:21:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有过难熬的时候吗  毛头小子\NYou've had some tough times, too, 28?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.71,0:21:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没人理解你作为一个英俊的成功人士是何感受吗\NNobody understands what it's like to be so good-looking and successful?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.27,0:21:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被保姆和管家抚养大的\NI was raised by nannies and housekeepers.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.52,0:21:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天呐\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.13,0:21:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是个混蛋\NYou're an ass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.43,0:21:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想说你经历的痛苦\NYour point is you didn't suffer
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.02,0:21:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是因为你英俊聪明\Nbecause you were good-looking and smart --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.89,0:22:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是因为你很有钱\Nyou suffered because you were rich?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.84,0:22:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有在圣诞节我才能见到我的父母\NThe only time I ever saw my parents was Christmas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.95,0:22:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,认真的吗  还要继续说\NSeriously, the story continues?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.03,0:22:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们每年都举行盛大的宴会\NThey had this big party every year,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.24,0:22:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管他们走到哪里  都会为了宴会飞回来\Nand wherever they were traveling they'd always fly home for it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.17,0:22:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也必须回家\NAnd I'd have to come home, too,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.74,0:22:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论他们把我送到了哪个学校\Nfrom whatever school they sent me off to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.44,0:22:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我18岁的时候  我厌倦了这种生活\NWhen I was 18, I decided that I was fed up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.84,0:22:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是一个男人  不想当他们的儿子了\NI was a man, done being their son.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.77,0:22:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我准备公开告诉他们\NAnd I was gonna tell them publicly,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.53,0:22:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉他们的朋友们他们有多可怕\Ntell all their friends what horrible people they were.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.74,0:22:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我从学校回到家  敲了敲门\NSo I came home from school, and I knocked on the door,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.75,0:22:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人开了门\Nand someone answered.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.63,0:22:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不是我的父母  是一个陌生人\NBut it wasn't my parents. It was a stranger.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.52,0:22:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到他们在数月前就卖掉了房子\NTurns out they'd sold the house months ago.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.59,0:22:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们走了\NThey were gone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.08,0:22:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我猜他们也受够了我吧\NI guess they were done with me, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.47,0:23:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了给利亚姆准备腹腔镜检查\NTo prep Liam for the laparoscopy,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.96,0:23:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们需要在他的胃里开四个小切口\Nwe need to make four small incisions in his stomach.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.74,0:23:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不需要做这个\NI don't need to do it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.03,0:23:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不需要做这个\NI-I don't need to do it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.52,0:23:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-利亚姆  你需要做  -我不需要\N- Liam, you do need to. - I don't need to!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.49,0:23:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要坚持几秒钟就好  利亚姆\NIf you could just hold still for a second, Liam.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.94,0:23:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公车司机让我下车\NThe -- the bus driver lets me off.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.08,0:23:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我迷路了\NI-I get lost --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.40,0:23:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在安全了\NYou're safe now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.28,0:23:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我迷路了  我很饿\NI get lost. I'm hungry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.84,0:23:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没法做饭\NI can't make food.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.11,0:23:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没法洗澡  不需要做这个\NC-C-Can't do bath -- Don't need to do it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.63,0:23:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没法做饭  没法穿衣服\NC-C-Can't do food -- C-Can't put on clothes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.06,0:23:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没法坐公交车\NCan't do bus.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.03,0:23:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我坐过公交车\NI took the bus.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.42,0:23:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在错误的站台下了车\NI got off at the wrong stop,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.53,0:23:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很害怕  但接着我找到了方向\Nand I got scared, but then I found my way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做过一次核磁共振  让人受伤了\NI did an MRI, and a man got hurt.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.12,0:23:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我犯了一个错误  我犯过很多错误\NI made a mistake. I make a lot of mistakes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.29,0:23:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你试着去走路\NYou tried to walk.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.60,0:23:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你犯了一个错误\NYou made a mistake.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.08,0:23:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但犯错是好事  你应该多犯一些错\NBut mistakes are good. You should make more.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.49,0:24:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很像我\NYou're like me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.55,0:24:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有红眼  眼色素层炎\NYou have red eyes -- uveitis.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.48,0:24:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利亚姆吃维生素\NLiam takes vitamins --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.96,0:24:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利亚姆也吃草药补充品吗\NDoes Liam also take herbal supplements?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.98,0:24:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡瓦根  怎么了\NKava root. Why?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.66,0:24:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不需要做腹腔镜手术\NHe doesn't need the laparoscopic surgery.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.57,0:24:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道他怎么了\NI know what's wrong with him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.08,0:24:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的红眼  是由免疫系统冲突造成的\NThe red eyes -- they're caused by an immune flare-up,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.96,0:24:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也会产生我们在他的消化系统中看到的瘢痕\Nwhich can create the scarring that we're seeing in his digestive system.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.73,0:24:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,治疗方案需要我们进入腹腔\NThe solution requires us to go in
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.52,0:24:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一片片摘除掉肠道上的受损部位\Nand remove damaged segments of the bowel piece by piece.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.95,0:24:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们\NUs?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.96,0:24:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的  我和我的团队\NYes, myself and my team.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.25,0:24:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫菲医生在你的团队吗\NIs Dr. Murphy on your team?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.97,0:24:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然\NOf course.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.75,0:24:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感谢你诊断我们的儿子\NThank you for diagnosing our son.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.25,0:24:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅伦德斯医生  我们同意你做这个手术\NDr. Melendez, you have our permission to do the surgery,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.01,0:24:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但莫菲医生不能参与其中\Nbut in no way will Dr. Murphy be in it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.42,0:25:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,患者的父母  他们不让步\NWell, the parents -- they won't budge.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.04,0:25:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们不信任患了自闭症的人\NThey don't believe that anyone who has autism
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.64,0:25:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有能力进行手术\Nis capable do doing surgery.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.01,0:25:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很显然  他们很荒谬\NWell, clearly they're irrational --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.95,0:25:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说不好  肤浅的人们\NI don't know -- shallow-minded people.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.27,0:25:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁在乎他自不自闭  有什么区别吗\NWho cares? What's the difference?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.96,0:25:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你同意他们的观点  对吗\NYou agree with them, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.84,0:25:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你同意他们吗\NDo you agree with them?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.22,0:25:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我的团队  我不希望任何人来告诉我\NIt's my team -- I don't want anybody telling me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.90,0:25:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁应该在我的团队里\Nwho's supposed to be on my team,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.33,0:25:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是董事会\Nincluding the Board.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.90,0:25:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没有回答我的问题\NYou're not answering my question.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.56,0:25:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个问题没有意义\NThe question's moot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.35,0:25:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有意义  并不是\NMoot? No, it's not.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.67,0:25:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你同意他们的观点\NIf you agree with them,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.64,0:25:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么唯一的问题就是有人踩到了你的痛处\Nthen the only issue is somebody stepping on your poor, little toes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.71,0:25:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克服它  然后去救那个孩子\NGet over it and go save the kid.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.70,0:25:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不同意\NIf you don't agree,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.87,0:25:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你认为肖恩能够进行手术\Nif you think Shaun can handle surgery,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.64,0:25:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就告诉他们\Nthen tell them that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.42,0:25:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他们哪凉快去哪儿\NTell them to go screw themselves.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.91,0:25:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们要么同意莫菲医生和你一起做手术\NEither they agree that Dr. Murphy belongs in that room with you,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.95,0:25:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要么就去别的地方做手术\Nor you can go find them someplace else to do the surgery.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.62,0:25:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时我18岁  举目无亲  身无分文\NI was an 18-year-old with no one and no money.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.16,0:25:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我打三份工  然后贷了款\NSo I worked three jobs and took out loans.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.98,0:26:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没死呢\NStill alive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.04,0:26:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故事不错  毛头小子\NThat's not a bad story, 28.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.81,0:26:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父母怎么样了\NWhat happened with the parents?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.42,0:26:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我和他们有联系  但是...\NI talk to them now, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.25,0:26:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮我走到现在的人不是他们\Nthey're not the people who got me here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:24.80,0:26:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是我从没想到的人\NIt was the people I didn't expect --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.41,0:26:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避难所的前海军给了我第一份工作\Nthe ex-Marine at the shelter who got me my first job,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:29.54,0:26:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后有个疯狂的艺术女孩\Nand this crazy artist girl
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:31.95,0:26:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说服我去追求我的梦想\Nwho convinced me to go after what I really wanted.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.96,0:26:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当你觉得孤身一人时  格伦\NWhen you think you're alone, Glen,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.52,0:26:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实你并不孤单\Nyou're not.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.09,0:26:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.80,0:26:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「好吧」\NAll right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:02.08,0:27:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备好了吗\NReady?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.12,0:27:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二  三\NTwo, three!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.24,0:27:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没做不安的梦吗\NNo disturbing dreams?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:07.57,0:27:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都值了36小时的班\NAfter a 36-hour shift?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:10.17,0:27:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从我躺到床上那一刻\NFrom the moment my head hits the pillow
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.89,0:27:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到醒来那一刻\Nto the moment wake up,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:13.55,0:27:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一夜无梦\Nall I see is black.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.43,0:27:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的注意力怎么样\NHow's your level of concentration?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.95,0:27:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有难以集中注意力吗\NHave you had any difficulty focusing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:20.06,0:27:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以一口气做完《纽约时报》的填字游戏\NI mean, I can do the New York Times crossword puzzle in one sitting.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.02,0:27:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然  有时我会希望自己更专注些\NSure, sometimes I wish I was more focused.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.70,0:27:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很正常吧\NIt's pretty normal, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.59,0:27:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肖恩与众不同\NShaun's different.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:38.52,0:27:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也有学者综合征\NHe also has savant syndrome.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.11,0:27:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他记忆超群\NHe has a remarkable memory.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:42.04,0:27:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有自闭症  跟我们的儿子一样\NHe has autism, same as our son --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.16,0:27:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同样的局限性\Nsame limitations.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:46.54,0:27:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也看到做核磁共振时我儿子的状态\NYou saw what happened to our son in the MRI --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.65,0:27:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他知道该安静地躺着  但他做不到\Nhe knew he needed to lie still, but he couldn't.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:51.65,0:27:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是莫菲医生在给我儿子动手术时\NNow, what happens if Dr. Murphy breaks down like that
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:54.51,0:27:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也像那样行为失控了呢\Nwhile he's standing over my son at an operating table?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.87,0:27:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你了解你的儿子\NYou know your son.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:00.25,0:28:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我了解外科医生\NI know surgeons.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:02.40,0:28:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在跟莫菲医生共事之后\NAnd after working with Dr. Murphy,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:04.12,0:28:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在手术台和其他地方质疑他之后\Nafter challenging him in surgery and everywhere else --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:08.34,0:28:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许他值得更多尊重\Nprobably more than he deserved --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.32,0:28:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以说我对他信心十足\NI can tell you he has my compete confidence.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.50,0:28:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:23.34,0:28:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们对他没信心\NHe doesn't have ours.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:25.82,0:28:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我们现在怎么办\NSo, what do we do now?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:28.80,0:28:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我联系了圣约瑟夫的同事\NI've contacted my colleague at St. Joseph's,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.86,0:28:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟她介绍了利亚姆的情况\Nupdated her on Liam's condition.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:33.27,0:28:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里的医生很厉害\NThey have good people.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:35.58,0:28:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可以尽快安排转院\NWe can arrange for transportation as soon as possible.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.18,0:28:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的手机在哪  看见我的手机了吗\NWhere's my phone? Have you seen my phone?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.02,0:28:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的第二个包呢  装着他的药的\NWhere's his second bag, the one with his medications?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:44.33,0:28:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想...\NI want...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:47.11,0:28:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想...\NI want...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:50.09,0:28:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了  宝贝\NWhat, honey?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:51.57,0:28:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说了我可以的\NHe said I could do it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.50,0:28:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要肖恩医生\NI want Dr. Shaun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:04.63,0:29:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的起搏器到了\NYour pacemaker's here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:05.62,0:29:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此刻已经在测试它了\NThe techs are programming it as we speak.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:07.74,0:29:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦准备好了  就给你装进去\NThe moment they're ready, we're gonna put it in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:21.95,0:29:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我之前说我的妻子去世了\NI told you my wife died.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:26.18,0:29:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实是她抛弃了我\NThe truth is s-she left me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:32.50,0:29:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但她抛弃我也情有可原\NBut I gave her good reason for that,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:35.05,0:29:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我该得的\Nso I got what I deserved.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:39.23,0:29:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-我们都... -但你没得到该得的\N- We all make -- But you didn't get what you deserved --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.43,0:29:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你该有爱你的父母\Ngood parents who loved you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:48.29,0:29:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们很幸运生了你  杰瑞德\NThey were lucky to have you, Jared.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.41,0:30:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你似乎调整得很好\NYou appear remarkably well-adjusted.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.53,0:30:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:10.31,0:30:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是称赞\NThat's not a compliment.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.71,0:30:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对此感到担忧\NThat's my concern.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:14.38,0:30:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我猜每个人的反应都不一样\NWell, I assume everyone responds differently.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:17.45,0:30:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但每个人都有反应\NThe thing is everyone responds.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.08,0:30:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,严格来说\NStrictly speaking,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:23.10,0:30:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还不需要接受治疗\Nyou don't meet the criteria to be required to go into treatment
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.97,0:30:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者休假\Nor take a leave of absence,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:28.56,0:30:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我不会让你停职\Nso I'm not gonna ground you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:34.72,0:30:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是个坚强的女人  克莱尔\NYou're a strong woman, Claire,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.53,0:30:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而这个力量无疑帮助了你很多\Nand that strength has undoubtedly played a major role
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.30,0:30:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你走到今天\Nin getting you where you are.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:42.26,0:30:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果你对此事件压抑了自己的感情\NBut if you have suppressed feelings about this incident,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:46.24,0:30:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你需要说给别人听\Nyou need to find someone to share them with.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:48.96,0:30:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则  它们会吞噬你\NBecause if not, they will eat you up
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.06,0:30:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你有多坚强\Nno matter how strong you are.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.75,0:31:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  格伦  第二...\NAll right, Glen. Second ti--
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:04.54,0:31:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托\NCome on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.00,0:31:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:14.34,0:31:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这该是个非常有趣的手术\NIt should be a very interesting surgery.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:16.22,0:31:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很高兴有机会参加\NI'm glad I'm participating.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:21.08,0:31:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的血压降到最低点\NHis pressure is bottoming out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:22.72,0:31:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事\NWhat's happening?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.37,0:31:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他肯定肠穿孔了\NHis bowel must have perforated.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.98,0:31:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他进入感染性休克\NHe's going into septic shock.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.99,0:31:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个穿孔可能在任何地方\NThis perforation could be anywhere.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:32.16,0:31:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最快查看整条肠的最好方式是什么\NWhat's the best way to access the entire bowel as quickly as possible?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.29,0:31:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全长中线切开\NFull-length midline incision.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.79,0:31:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好  标记一下\NGood. Mark it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.96,0:31:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们切开之后要怎么做\NAnd what do we do once we get in there?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.51,0:31:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取出整条肠\NEviscerate the entire bowel
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.00,0:31:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以彻底检查坏死的部分\Nso we can check every inch for necrotic segments.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:43.70,0:31:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  开始切开\NOkay, let's make the cut.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:51.25,0:31:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要不要负责切开\NYou gonna take it or not?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:15.84,0:32:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是3L号手术刀\NThis is the Number 3 L.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:17.84,0:32:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高碳钢制成  不会折断\NIt's made of high carbon steel. It doesn't break.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:21.16,0:32:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错  莫菲医生\NThat's correct, Dr. Murphy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:35.77,0:32:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,切开时间  下午2:05\NTime of incision -- 2:05 p.m.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.70,0:32:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全面封锁\NWe have a code green --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:40.10,0:32:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,患者为白人男性  73岁\Npatient is a Caucasian male, 73 years of age.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:43.32,0:32:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他去哪里了\NWhere'd he go?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:45.72,0:32:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  我这就过去\NYeah, on my way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.38,0:32:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找到五公分长的近端空肠段\NI have a five-centimeter segment of proximal jejunum.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:54.36,0:32:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已硬化  但没穿孔\NIt's...sclerotic, but not perforated.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:55.78,0:32:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  标记然后继续\NAll right, mark it and move on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:57.93,0:32:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肖恩  你为什么傻站着\NShaun, why are you just standing there?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:58.91,0:33:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们还有八米的肠要查看\NWe have 25 feet of bowel to run.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:02.71,0:33:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肖恩  赶紧继续  除非你有发现\NShaun, you need to get moving -- unless you've found something.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:06.26,0:33:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-我找到穿孔了  -夹住它\N- I have the perforation. - Clamp it off --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:09.17,0:33:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会用肠切开剪去除受损部位\NI'll get in there with the enterotomy scissors and remove the damaged segment.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:13.08,0:33:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能\NI can't.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.45,0:33:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能  为什么\NYou can't? Why not?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.18,0:33:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是蜂窝织炎\NIt's a phlegmon.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:20.53,0:33:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你找到了透壁性脓肿\NYou found a walled-off abscess?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.90,0:33:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很大\NIt's large.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:23.01,0:33:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-别碰  -已经碰了\N- Don't touch it. - I already am.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.70,0:33:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你移动造成它破裂\NIf you move and that thing ruptures,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:26.38,0:33:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脓会扩散到他整个腹腔\Nthe pus will spread to his entire abdominal cavity --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.43,0:33:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,造成死亡\Nthis boy dies.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:29.28,0:33:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道  所以我没动\NI know, that's why I'm not moving.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:31.10,0:33:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克莱尔  你把它轻轻地打开\NClaire, I need you to open it up gently.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.87,0:33:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要除去脓毒含量\NI'm gonna evacuate the septic contents,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:34.65,0:33:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用抗生素冲洗腹腔\Nflush the cavity with antibiotics,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:36.31,0:33:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后我会让你移除胶囊\Nand then I'm gonna have you remove the capsule.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:39.07,0:33:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什么也没做\NI didn't do anything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.16,0:33:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血压在降到最低点\NThat's the pressure tanking.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:41.24,0:33:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须赶快完成\NYou need to finish what you're doing right now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:46.86,0:33:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赶紧  克莱尔  加油\NLet's go, Claire. Come on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:51.86,0:33:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夹住\NClamp.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.70,0:33:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们去看左边\NYou guys check left.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:05.54,0:34:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起来吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:06.08,0:34:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手\NStop.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:09.49,0:34:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了  格伦\NCome on, Glen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:11.19,0:34:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们能做到的\NWe can do this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.20,0:34:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想...\NI don't want to --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:13.66,0:34:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是不想\NI just don't want to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:15.16,0:34:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求你了  别管我\NPlease leave me alone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:19.27,0:34:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一有了力气  就爬起来跳下去\NOnce I get my strength back, I'll climb up and jump.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:24.87,0:34:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会让你那么做的\NI can't let you do that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:37.52,0:34:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当这个临时起搏器失效的时候\NWhen this temporary pacer fails,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:39.79,0:34:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它肯定会失效的\Nwhich it will,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:42.67,0:34:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心跳就会停止  你会突然死亡\Nyour heart may stop and you die suddenly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:45.90,0:34:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但更有可能的是  格伦\NBut more likely, Glen,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:46.83,0:34:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心率会减缓\Nyou slip back into that slow rhythm,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:49.00,0:34:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胸部剧痛\Nyour chest is racked with excruciating pain
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:51.18,0:34:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肺部开始充满液体\Nand your lungs start to fill with fluid,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.61,0:34:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会缓慢窒息\Nand slowly you suffocate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.91,0:34:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,省省吧  毛头小子\NGive it a rest, 28.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:57.02,0:34:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把不抢救预嘱拿来  再给我叫辆出租车就好了\NJust get me a DNR and a cab.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:00.14,0:35:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你帮不了我的\NYou can't help me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.93,0:35:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以\NYes, I can.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:24.82,0:35:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手术很艰难\NIt was a difficult procedure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:27.55,0:35:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们切除了...\NWe removed a total of two feet of --
